snippet.title: Arcade Game: Hi-Way 1975 (Atari) No Sound
snippet.description:
A driving game where you drive a car on the road to steer the wheel and use the accelerator to move the car and you move sidewise and vertically as you have to pass the cars running the same direction without crashing into them which come in front. Smashing the vehicles involves a monetary standstill. The score depends on the covered distance. 

Anyone interested in trying out this game, here it is:
http://adamulation.blogspot.com/

Note: Comments for gameplay videos with no sound are now disable because they video is subject to be reuploaded when ever sound is added to the game. Once the sound has been added, it will be reuploaded and comments will be enabled.
